Usage: clock_opt_design [-help] [-check_cts_config] [-cts] [-expandedViews]
                        [-num_paths <string>] [-out_dir <string>]
                        [-prefix <string>] [-timing_debug_report]

-help                       # Prints out the command usage
-check_cts_config           # Only check cts prerequisites, with no changes
                            # made to the design (bool, optional)
-cts                        # Build Clock Tree only  (bool, optional)
-expandedViews              # Expand View option  (bool, optional)
-num_paths <string>         # Specify the number of paths generated in timing
                            # reports (string, optional)
-out_dir <string>           # Output Directory option  (string, optional)
-prefix <string>            # File Name Prefix option  (string, optional)
-timing_debug_report        # Generate timing debug report (bool, optional)